@Comment:	Time is 2:31
@Comment:	Dear Sherry , I miss you and Zach. and we went to New york city last week. we went to the Top oF The world Trade center , and a parade and The central park zoo. see you at christmas! Love Chi P.S. we were on the 109th florr arf too Zach
@Comment:	MOT suggests writing to Chi's Aunt Sherry who lives in Wyoming. Zach is Aunt Sherry's dog. Mot and Chi collaborate on what to write , but Mot dictates how it should be written. Mot helps with spelling , which she does very quickly , and punctuation. At times it gets noisy with Bro in the background
